<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>お申し込みありがとうございます | 本、文通</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --yellow:     #E8C84A;
      --yellow-lt:  #F5E08A;
      --yellow-dk:  #C9A832;
      --green:      #4A6741;
      --green-lt:   #6A8B65;
      --cream:      #FDFAF3;
      --cream-dk:   #F4EDD8;
      --ink:        #1C1C1C;
      --ink-mid:    #3D3730;
      --ink-lt:     #7A7268;
      --white:      #FFFFFF;

      --f-display: 'Shippori Mincho', 'Yu Mincho', serif;
      --f-body:    'Noto Serif JP', 'Yu Mincho', serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--f-body);
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-size: 15px;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    .nav {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      background: rgba(253,250,243,0.92);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(232,200,74,0.25);
    }
    .nav-logo img { height: 36px; width: auto; vertical-align: middle; }

    /* ─── MAIN ─── */
    main {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 80px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .thanks-mark {
      font-size: 30px;
      color: var(--yellow-dk);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    }

    .thanks-label {
      font-family: var(--f-display);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      color: var(--yellow-dk);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .thanks-title {
      font-family: var(--f-display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .thanks-copy {
      max-width: 460px;
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 2.1;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .thanks-detail {
      max-width: 460px;
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--cream-dk);
      border-top: 3px solid var(--yellow);
      padding: 32px 36px;
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .thanks-detail p {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 2.0;
      color: var(--ink-mid);
    }
    .thanks-detail p + p { margin-top: 12px; }
    .thanks-detail strong { color: var(--ink); }

    .btn-primary {
      font-family: var(--f-display);
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      padding: 16px 44px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 2px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--green-lt); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      padding: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: var(--f-display);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      line-height: 2.2;
    }
    footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--yellow); }
    .footer-logo {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--yellow);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav { padding: 14px 20px; }
      main { padding: 64px 24px; }
      .thanks-detail { padding: 26px 24px; }
      footer { padding: 32px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <a class="nav-logo" href="https://mimosa.mimosa-partners.com/buntsu">
    <img src="/buntsu_logo.png" alt="本、文通">
  </a>
</nav>

<main>
  <p class="thanks-mark">✦</p>
  <p class="thanks-label">Thank You</p>
  <h1 class="thanks-title">お申し込み、<br>ありがとうございます。</h1>
  <p class="thanks-copy">
    お支払い登録が完了しました。<br>
    あなたのことを想いながら、最初の１冊を選びます。<br>
    本と手紙が届くまで、少しお待ちください。
  </p>

  <div class="thanks-detail">
    <p><strong>次回以降のお支払い</strong>：毎月10日に自動引き落とし</p>
    <p><strong>お届け</strong>：月末〜翌月初旬を目安に発送</p>
    <p><strong>ご連絡先</strong>：<a href="mailto:info@mimosa-partners.com" style="color:var(--green)">info@mimosa-partners.com</a></p>
  </div>

  <a class="btn-primary" href="https://mimosa.mimosa-partners.com/buntsu">「本、文通」のページに戻る</a>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-logo">出版社 ミモザ</div>
  <p><a href="https://mimosa.mimosa-partners.com">mimosa.mimosa-partners.com</a></p>
  <p style="margin-top:8px"><a href="mailto:info@mimosa-partners.com">info@mimosa-partners.com</a></p>
  <p style="margin-top:20px; font-size:11px">© 2026 ミモザパートナーズ合同会社</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
